 t access. Two-round selection: Round One closes 5 June 2026\; Round One no
 tification and Round Two invitations on 3 July 2026. Eligibility: nonprofi
 ts in Canada with a CRA-registered charitable organisation number (a 9-dig
 it Business Number\, often followed by RR0001 or similar). NOTE: this is a
