 ers\, or for-profit studios.\n\nOrganisation: Amazon Web Services (AWS Ima
 gine Grant Program)\nLocation: Canada (CRA-registered charitable organisat
 ions only)\nAward: Up to $75\,000 USD unrestricted cash + up to $25\,000 U
 SD in AWS Promotional Credits + AWS marketing support and access to AWS te
 chnical specialists\nDuration: Two-round process. Round One closes 5 June 
 2026\; notifications 3 July 2026 with Round Two invitations issued the sam
 e day.\n\nMore: https://aws.amazon.com/government-education/nonprofits/aws
 -imagine-grant-program/aws-imagine-grant-canada/?utm_source=artificialnouv
 eaugrantdesk&utm_medium=referral
